me taking place at the home of Olympiacos' rivals AEK Athens.\", \"from\": 176, \"to\": 387, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 357, \"end\": 367, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympiacos_F.C.\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.6602595654450224e-14, \"text\": \"Olympiacos\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympiacos_F.C.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympiacos_F.C.\"}, {\"begin\": 376, \"end\": 379, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/AEK_Athens_F.C.\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.3761582895829393e-15, \"text\": \"AEK\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/AEK_Athens_F.C.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/AEK_Athens_F.C.\"}, {\"begin\": 380, \"end\": 386, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Athens\", \"score\": 0.999982586923303, \"rank\": 1.7407377637465906e-05, \"text\": \"Athens\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Athens\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Athens\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"DETAILS\", \"from\": 187, \"to\": 194}, {\"ngram\": \"A forgettable final\", \"from\": 195, \"to\": 214}, {\"ngram\": \"life\", \"from\": 228, \"to\": 232}, {\"ngram\": \"just four minutes\", \"from\": 238, \"to\": 255}, {\"ngram\": \"extra time\", \"from\": 259, \"to\": 269}, {\"ngram\": \"El Kaabi\", \"from\": 283, \"to\": 291}, {\"ngram\": \"the only goal\", \"from\": 304, \"to\": 317}, {\"ngram\": \"a game\", \"from\": 321, \"to\": 327}, {\"ngram\": \"place\", \"from\": 335, \"to\": 340}, {\"ngram\": \"the home\", \"from\": 344, \"to\": 352}]}, {\"sentence\": \"While the Greek side could celebrate becoming the first team from their country to win a European trophy, Fiorentina were once again left wondering what might have been a year after losing in the final to West Ham.\", \"from\": 389, \"to\": 603, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 399, \"end\": 404, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greek_language\", \"score\": 0.8897973406722295, \"rank\": 0.12379103060505789, \"text\": \"Greek\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greek_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greek_language\"}, {\"begin\": 495, \"end\": 505, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ACF_Fiorentina\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.954848475783103e-32, \"text\": \"Fiorentina\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ACF_Fiorentina\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ACF_Fiorentina\"}, {\"begin\": 599, \"end\": 602, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ham\", \"score\": 0.9999999999990905, \"rank\": 7.286589826801506e-13, \"text\": \"Ham\", \"types\": [\"Q2095\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ham\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ham\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the first team\", \"from\": 435, \"to\": 449}, {\"ngram\": \"their country\", \"from\": 455, \"to\": 468}, {\"ngram\": \"a European trophy\", \"from\": 476, \"to\": 493}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A lengthy VAR check followed El Kaabi's effort but it survived a potential offside to settle a final that had failed to burst into life until that point.\", \"from\": 605, \"to\": 758, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 615, \"end\": 618, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Video_assistant_referee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.091871621564919e-34, \"text\": \"VAR\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Video_assistant_referee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Video_assistant_referee\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"El Kaabi's effort\", \"from\": 634, \"to\": 651}, {\"ngram\": \"a potential offside\", \"from\": 668, \"to\": 687}, {\"ngram\": \"a final\", \"from\": 698, \"to\": 705}, {\"ngram\": \"life\", \"from\": 736, \"to\": 740}, {\"ngram\": \"that point\", \"from\": 747, \"to\": 757}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Fiorentina had not been so lucky earlier in the game.\", \"from\": 760, \"to\": 813, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 760, \"end\": 770, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ACF_Fiorentina\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.954848475783103e-32, \"text\": \"Fiorentina\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ACF_Fiorentina\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ACF_Fiorentina\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the game\", \"from\": 804, \"to\": 812}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Italians thought they had broken the deadlock with just 10 minutes on the clock when defender Nikola Milenkovic turned home only for it to be ruled out for offside.\", \"from\": 814, \"to\": 982, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 818, \"end\": 826, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy\", \"score\": 0.9934258995980397, \"rank\": 0.004402535876285896, \"text\": \"Italians\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the deadlock\", \"from\": 851, \"to\": 863}, {\"ngram\": \"just 10 minutes\", \"from\": 869, \"to\": 884}, {\"ngram\": \"the clock\", \"from\": 888, \"to\": 897}, {\"ngram\": \"defender Nikola Milenkovic\", \"from\": 903, \"to\": 929}, {\"ngram\": \"offside\", \"from\": 974, \"to\": 981}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Nicolas Gonzalez miscued when presented with a fine chance for Fiorentina towards the end of a tight first half that unsurprisingly ended goalless.\", \"from\": 984, \"to\": 1131, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1047, \"end\": 1057, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ACF_Fiorentina\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.954848475783103e-32, \"text\": \"Fiorentina\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ACF_Fiorentina\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ACF_Fiorentina\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Nicolas Gonzalez\", \"from\": 984, \"to\": 1000}, {\"ngram\": \"a fine chance\", \"from\": 1029, \"to\": 1042}, {\"ngram\": \"the end\", \"from\": 1066, \"to\": 1073}, {\"ngram\": \"a tight first half that unsurprisingly ended goalless\", \"from\": 1077, \"to\": 1130}]}, {\"sentence\": \"With little goalmouth action to speak of it was the Serie A side who were carving out more opportunities, but Christian Kouame was the next player to fluff his lines when in a good position.\", \"from\": 1133, \"to\": 1323, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1185, \"end\": 1192, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serie_A\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.8893000281234677e-21, \"text\": \"Serie A\", \"types\": [\"Q623109\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serie_A\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serie_A\"}, {\"begin\": 1243, \"end\": 1252, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christian_Cage\", \"score\": 0.9220039834988973, \"rank\": 0.07222048748420162, \"text\": \"Christian\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13474373\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christian_Cage\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christian_Cage\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"little goalmouth action\", \"from\": 1138, \"to\": 1161}, {\"ngram\": \"more opportunities\", \"from\": 1219, \"to\": 1237}, {\"ngram\": \"the next player\", \"from\": 1264, \"to\": 1279}, {\"ngram\": \"his lines\", \"from\": 1289, \"to\": 1298}, {\"ngram\": \"a good position\", \"from\": 1307, \"to\": 1322}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Olympiacos stood firm and starting carving out chances of their own but Vicente Iborra could only glance a header wide as the Europa Conference League final went to an extra period for the first time.\", \"from\": 1325, \"to\": 1525, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1325, \"end\": 1335, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympiacos_F.C.\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.6602595654450224e-14, \"text\": \"Olympiacos\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympiacos_F.C.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympiacos_F.C.\"}, {\"begin\": 1397, \"end\": 1411, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vicente_Iborra\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Vicente Iborra\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vicente_Iborra\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vicente_Iborra\"}, {\"begin\": 1458, \"end\": 1475, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UEFA_Europa_Conference_League\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.804701621418366e-42, \"text\": \"Conference League\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UEFA_Europa_Conference_League\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UEFA_Europa_Conference_League\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"chances\", \"from\": 1372, \"to\": 1379}, {\"ngram\": \"an extra period\", \"from\": 1490, \"to\": 1505}, {\"ngram\": \"the first time\", \"from\": 1510, \"to\": 1524}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Substitute Stevan Jovetic, a former Fiorentina forward, forced a smart save out of Pietro Terracciano but the moment of individual quality needed to settle the tie was moments away.\", \"from\": 1527, \"to\": 1708, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1527, \"end\": 1537, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Substitute_(association_football)\", \"score\": 0.9171971918781212, \"rank\": 0.06617941976022838, \"text\": \"Substitute\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Substitute_(association_football)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Substitute_(association_football)\"}, {\"begin\": 1538, \"end\": 1544, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stevan_Dedijer\", \"score\": 0.9999989820790411, \"rank\": 8.057520318710958e-07, \"text\": \"Stevan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stevan_Dedijer\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stevan_Dedijer\"}, {\"begin\": 1610, \"end\": 1628, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pietro_Terracciano\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Pietro Terracciano\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pietro_Terracciano\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pietro_Terracciano\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a smart save\", \"from\": 1590, \"to\": 1602}, {\"ngram\": \"the moment\", \"from\": 1633, \"to\": 1643}, {\"ngram\": \"individual quality\", \"from\": 1647, \"to\": 1665}, {\"ngram\": \"the tie\", \"from\": 1683, \"to\": 1690}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A memorable season for El Kaabi - who scored five times across the semi-final win over Aston Villa - was topped off with his 33rd goal of the campaign, prompting wild celebrations just down the road in Piraeus as he stooped to head home Santiago Hezze's cross.\", \"from\": 1710, \"to\": 1970, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1797, \"end\": 1808, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aston_Villa_F.C.\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.647538843678302e-16, \"text\": \"Aston Villa\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aston_Villa_F.C.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aston_Villa_F.C.\"}, {\"begin\": 1912, \"end\": 1919, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Karaiskakis_Stadium\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.618441431619631e-19, \"text\": \"Piraeus\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Karaiskakis_Stadium\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Karaiskakis_Stadium\"}, {\"begin\": 1947, \"end\": 1955, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Santiago\", \"score\": 0.9996763802507388, \"rank\": 0.00018217418171574443, \"text\": \"Santiago\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Santiago\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Santiago\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A memorable season\", \"from\": 17